{"tid":2305524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭承認港共用現金出人工＝將港共政府同三大發鈔銀行送上金融制裁","createTime":"2020-11-29T16:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T06:34:18.000Z","uid":33263,"like":69,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6d772d3682212515f0a61c81303e27da087c65","tid":2305524,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭承認港府用現金發工資即將給美制裁港府和港銀行工具<br />\n1.政府係自己既銀行户口提供現金俾林鄭<br />\n呢點等於銀行曲線同林鄭做交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ge.usembassy.gov/new-u-s-sanctions-seek-to-block-iranian-regimes-weapons-programs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fge.usembassy.gov%2Fnew-u-s-sanctions-seek-to-block-iranian-regimes-weapons-programs%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=a368e02f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ge.usembassy.gov/new-u-s-sanctions-seek-to-block-iranian-regimes-weapons-programs/</a><br />\n<br />\n2.需要有美元才能夠發行港元<br />\n任何港元既交易都係應該禁止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭自爆自己收現金 等於明確話俾美國知 港共刻意避開美國制裁<br />\n反證有銀行同港共合作 出糧俾幾位港共官員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁即係話secondary sanction一定會來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db126dff2f70c6391f8ca330fa96dbbc5e475cb4","tid":2305524,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"睇左陣路德正想出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42430837d6545cffd6a6e47bb3f7bbde5983a545","tid":2305524,"uid":33263,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"db126dff2f70c6391f8ca330fa96dbbc5e475cb4","tid":2305524,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"睇左陣路德正想出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"路德呢個位有道理<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊間銀行出現金俾林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國佬如果查唔到 就可能直接制裁三間發鈔銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接港元同美元脫勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2fc728b91372a02f86749d3c01647019010144","tid":2305524,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db126dff2f70c6391f8ca330fa96dbbc5e475cb4","tid":2305524,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"睇左陣路德正想出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1STjDFxxjjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1STjDFxxjjw&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=c93ce30c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1STjDFxxjjw</a><br />\n11/29/2020 路德時評（路安墨談）：美眾議院即將通過清理所有中共控制在美上市公司法案！為什麼林鄭承認港府用現金發工資即將給美制裁港府和港銀行工具；"},{"pid":"903a4c21312dd2396da22acaaa0d5d6aaf9fbab4","tid":2305524,"uid":84116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"中銀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32406197270b22c3d6e777f718f3486f94d72c1b","tid":2305524,"uid":283207,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":